Make sure to execute this script within your MYSQL folder, or where ever if it's in your environment variable

Welcome to Search and Replace in Database
You should enter the following arguments
-s [--search] search a text in database/table
-r [--replace] replace this text search a text in database/table
-u [--user] user name of the database
-p [--password] password of the database
-d [--database] name of the database

Optional:
-t [--table] name of the table



P.S 
I wrote this simple script after I changed the domain in my Wiki. 
